{"tid":1797165,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【魂斷西班牙】英女童度假村泳池遇溺 父兄落水拯救三人齊喪命","createTime":"2019-12-25T07:54:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T08:00:30.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a64a8dd5d26b1017fec77d53ffa0a1252145736a","tid":1797165,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T07:54:30.000Z","msg":"西班牙南部一個泳池平安夜發生悲劇，一個英國家庭三名成員遇溺身亡。<br />\n事發於馬拉加附近的Costa del Sol度假村。當地傳媒引述目擊者指，9歲英國女童先遇溺，其53歲父親和16歲兄長落水救她時也遇溺。女童母親報警，國民衞隊派出的蛙人趕到現場，但只見三人浮屍池中。<br />\n警方正調查事發經過，並派心理學家輔導死者家屬。<br />\n英國《每日鏡報》報道，警方正檢查泳池的抽水系統。報道指，一名英國男童2009年在泰國水上樂園游泳時，被吸入抽水系統，導致溺斃。<br />\n今年8月，一名12歲俄羅斯女孩在土耳其一個酒店泳池游水時，被池中的強力抽水系統吸住，被困水下15分鐘，最終身亡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191225/large/1577228182_6d9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191225%2Flarge%2F1577228182_6d9b.jpg&h=9e3e2028&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蛙人到場時，發現三人已經溺斃。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191225/60415096\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191225%2F60415096&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFGFzq3Uwi%2FWN07E9MureYdc%3D&h=b75bf848\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191225%2F60415096&h=18839287\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191225/60415096</a>"},{"pid":"803693bfdcba3f257b017f4247403a282a1a17e4","tid":1797165,"uid":215794,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T07:58:27.000Z","msg":"雖然rip<br />\n但我想關心香港事多啲"},{"pid":"20ba5d4ab51e91088ed4706a1633acff33262a0e","tid":1797165,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T08:00:09.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"fa7c5f19655652c489d9b7af8928b62ec307c361","tid":1797165,"uid":4574,"like":0,"